In Swooni crosses the lives of six men together in a luxury hotel. While a heat wave the city sneaks, emotions run high. Anna and Henry have it all: a teenage son, a good job, a nice house. The wedding of Anna's sister, however, makes them think about the choices they made??. Henry is happy with what he has. But Anna wonders if something more needs to be. Violet wants to reconcile with her before she dies daughter Vicky, who works in the hotel chambermaid. But Vicky does not seem inclined to settle the conflict lay. She looks after Joyeux, a small African refugee who is hiding in the hotel for the police. When Amadou, Joyeux's father, shows up at the hotel in search of his son, becomes the fate of each of these characters inextricably linked with that of the others. Until the rain and the heat breaks for redemption will.

